      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:05",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "你tm疯了吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "11:05",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "还说我今天有问题",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "11:05",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "我今天看到一个好玩的东西",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:03",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "“人类无法共情年轻的自己”",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:03",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "如果能看到自己的过去：“孩子，你是错的，你不应该走这条路”，",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:04",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "过去的自己看到现在的自己：“你懦弱了，老东西”",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:05",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "你今年几岁啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:10",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "我24",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:10",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "那你是前辈了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:11",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "我现在还没见到过我脑子让我失望过",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:11",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "但我觉得我能从很多年龄大的人那里学到东西",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:12",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "特别是我老师啊，感觉各路神仙都知道",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:12",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "你懦弱了老东西",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:12",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "欸年轻就是好啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:12",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "那。。。。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:13",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "你跟我说一下你的感想吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:13",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "我想听",
