      "timestamp": "12:41",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "之后啥东西的再说",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:41",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "但是我遇见了很多坎，待人处事也有问题",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:41",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "。。。。主要是我在生活中找到合伙人，找到方向的能力感觉缺失了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:42",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "就。。。。。我知道是我的环境问题。我没有遇见同样和我一样有追求的人，但是我同时又有很多莫名其妙的事要干",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:42",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "哇你在做公司啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:42",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "那一定很有给自己干活的感觉才对啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:42",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "你感觉触碰不到自己的梦想了么？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:42",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "还是陷入短时幸福漩涡了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:43",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "短时幸福漩涡是啥玩意",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:43",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": " short dopamine rushes",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:44",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "当代人很容易陷入的因努力没有成果而刷视频导致的漩涡",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:44",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "不去交流 不去发现躺平当咸鱼",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:44",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "你在教我做人？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:44",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "额。。。科学现象啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:44",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "好心开导你看开一点",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:45",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "我找茬都想不出你这在想啥",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:45",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "哈哈开个玩笑。",
