      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:45",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "但努力了没看到成果是真的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:45",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "但你也知道不努力就不会有成果对吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:45",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "好好想想怎么努力，或者怎么认识怎么努力",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:45",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "加油",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:45",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "[[sticker:uploads/upload_1773367131784861000.gif]]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:46",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "话说你这么丧网上罚你给我讲故事",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:46",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "不讲个你喜欢的故事我下次不跟你讲话了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:46",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "好吧好吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:47",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "又不是每天都有好故事",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:47",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "那你去搜一个么",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:47",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "hmmf",
