      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "12:47",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "哈哈",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:49",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "喂喂喂",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "09:00",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "查收故事集",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "[[sticker:uploads/upload_1771863303700818125.jpg]]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "从前有个城市",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "这个城市里的所有工作都被ai替代了，人们只能验证ai做的工作有没有出错",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "可能一个人一年只能查到10个错误",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "但每个人都去工作",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "到这里你有什么想问的么",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "这个国家为什么会允许这么多人活着？企业不会把他们开出么？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "为了延续",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为其他不给普通人工作的国家都因为没有人而灭亡了。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "这很现实主义",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "请继续",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "在这个国家里，创新被停滞，因为教育并没有宣扬创新的必要，也不知道怎么去创新",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "国民过着日复一日的没效率和追求的工作",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "但他们看起来很幸福，但同样虚无",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "听起来不像一个故事",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "这个是一个国家",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "这个国家达到了最后的发展，他们达到了一种状态。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "他们还活着，仍然有人。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "你觉得，这样的社会是你愿意看到的么",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "不愿意",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "创新被停滞了我会想死",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "但如果只是工作内容枯燥但有自由分配的时间的话",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得这个社会也会是一个好的社会。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "但以我现在的状态过去我觉得我能过得很滋润",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "你呢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "在这样的社会发展到之前",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "明智的国家会制造制度强行把利益分给能制造这样社会的人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "不明智的国家会在即得利益面前讨好上面那样的国家",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "结果呢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "听起来和你幸福的象征没有区别",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
